'''EMI音樂出版'''（{{lang-en|EMI Music Publishing}}）是一家總部設在[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]的[[跨國公司|跨國]][[音樂出版社|音樂出版社]]，由[[索尼/聯合電視音樂出版|索尼/聯合電視音樂出版]]拥有，是這個全球最大音樂出版集團的一個部分。

== 歷史 ==
[[EMI|EMI]]在1958年進軍音樂出版行業，成立阿德莫爾及比奇伍德，即EMI音樂出版的前身<ref name="Ardmore">{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=JQkEAAAAMBAJ&pg=RA1-PA29&lpg=RA1-PA29&dq=Ardmore+and+Beechwood+emi+1958&source=bl&ots=YZpGVDouyd&sig=Luvel81ARV8SpQqsLlGX9ahttkQ&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0CCQQ6AEwAWoVChMIiLOHrO32xgIVxhmmCh2HZQoU#v=onepage&q=Ardmore%20and%20Beechwood%20emi%201958&f=false|title=150,000 titles in world music publishing|date=1 September 1973|publisher=Billboard|language=en|accessdate=25 July 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304080845/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=JQkEAAAAMBAJ&pg=RA1-PA29&lpg=RA1-PA29&dq=Ardmore+and+Beechwood+emi+1958&source=bl&ots=YZpGVDouyd&sig=Luvel81ARV8SpQqsLlGX9ahttkQ&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0CCQQ6AEwAWoVChMIiLOHrO32xgIVxhmmCh2HZQoU#v=onepage&q=Ardmore%20and%20Beechwood%20emi%201958&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。EMI在1969年以120萬美元及70,000股普通股收購基斯普勞斯音樂，大幅擴大他們在音樂出版方面的業務，又在1973年以875萬美元收購聯合音樂出版社<ref name="Ardmore"/>。

EMI在1974年把其音樂出版業務更名為EMI音樂出版<ref name="rename">{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=jim-YANOn5AC&pg=RA8-PA14&lpg=RA8-PA14&dq=1974+EMI+Music+Publishing&source=bl&ots=uUe0CbW6R3&sig=4RujR5riRezIBaSZ_W8YcVL79Mw&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0CC4Q6AEwA2oVChMIqLLVpvH2xgIVhtimCh0fOwca#v=onepage&q=1974%20EMI%20Music%20Publishing&f=false|title=With a Litte Help From My Friends|date=26 November 2011|publisher=Billboard|language=en|accessdate=25 July 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304092227/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=jim-YANOn5AC&pg=RA8-PA14&lpg=RA8-PA14&dq=1974+EMI+Music+Publishing&source=bl&ots=uUe0CbW6R3&sig=4RujR5riRezIBaSZ_W8YcVL79Mw&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0CC4Q6AEwA2oVChMIqLLVpvH2xgIVhtimCh0fOwca#v=onepage&q=1974%20EMI%20Music%20Publishing&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1976年，EMI音樂出版從[[哥倫比亞電影公司|哥倫比亞電影公司]]收購幕寶及克金斯的庫藏，成為電影音樂的主要出版商<ref name="rename"/>。

2011年5月，EMI音樂出版從[[美國作曲家、作家和發行商協會|美國作曲家、作家和發行商協會]]手裡得到約200,000首歌曲的機械及同步版權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/emi-music-publishing-taking-licensing-184688|title=EMI Music Publishing Taking Over Licensing Digital Rights From ASCAP|last=Christman|first=Ed|date=4 May 2011|publisher=Hollywood Reporter|language=en|accessdate=25 July 2015|archive-date=2013-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605100133/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/emi-music-publishing-taking-licensing-184688|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年11月，[[索尼/聯合電視音樂出版|索尼/聯合電視音樂出版]]領導的財團（包括美國索尼、邁克爾·傑克遜遺產管理委員會、穆巴達拉發展公司、晉瑋金融有限公司、黑石集團旗下的GSO資本及[[大衛·葛芬|大衛·葛芬]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/18/business/media/sony-plans-major-layoffs-of-emi-work-force.html?_r=1|title=Sony Plans Major Cuts in EMI Jobs|last=Sisario|first=Ben|date=17 April 2012|publisher=The New York Times|language=en|accessdate=25 July 2015|archive-date=2013-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130413053149/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/18/business/media/sony-plans-major-layoffs-of-emi-work-force.html?_r=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>）作價22億美元收購[[花旗集團|花旗集團]]的EMI音樂出版<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/11/12/business/media/emi-is-sold-for-4-1-billion-consolidating-the-music-industry.html?adxnnl=1&adxnnlx=1365256532-ZPTirKfBwt1JFT+j75xJnw|title=EMI Is Sold for $4.1 Billion in Combined Deals, Consolidating the Music Industry|last=Sisario|first=Ben|date=11 November 2011|publisher=New York Times|language=en|accessdate=26 July 2015|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402234007/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/11/12/business/media/emi-is-sold-for-4-1-billion-consolidating-the-music-industry.html?adxnnl=1&adxnnlx=1365256532-ZPTirKfBwt1JFT+j75xJnw|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/nov/12/business/la-fi-ct-emi-sold-20111112-68|title=EMI Group sold as two separate pieces to Universal Music and Sony|last=Pham|first=Alex|date=12 November 2011|publisher=Los Angeles Times|language=en|accessdate=26 July 2015|archive-date=2015-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150516070801/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/nov/12/business/la-fi-ct-emi-sold-20111112-68|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有關收購在2012年4月獲得[[歐洲聯盟委員會|歐洲聯盟委員會]]的接納{{cfn|Wueller|y=2013|p=589}}，但條件是收購方要放棄英國[[著名音樂|著名音樂]]、歐洲維京、英國維京音樂出版及美國維京四個音樂目錄及12位當代音樂作家的作品，包括[[致命情人|致命情人]]、[[蓋瑞·巴洛|蓋瑞·巴洛]]、[[本·哈珀|本·哈珀]]、[[初哥樂隊|初哥樂隊]]、[[藍尼·克羅維茲|藍尼·克羅維茲]]、[[奧齊·奧斯本|奧齊·奧斯本]]、[[Placebo|安慰劑]]及[[羅比·威廉斯|羅比·威廉斯]]。上述的音樂目錄統稱為「羅塞塔」，在2012年12月被[[BMG_音樂版權管理公司|BMG 音樂版權管理公司]]收購。在得到美國反壟斷當局的批准之下，索尼/聯合電視音樂出版財團的收購得以在2012年6月完成<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/bmg-buys-virgin-famous-music-406080|title=BMG Buys Virgin, Famous Music Catalog From Sony/ATV|last=Roxborough|first=Scott|date=21 December 2012|publisher=Hollywood Reporter|language=en|accessdate=26 July 2015|archive-date=2018-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614045755/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/bmg-buys-virgin-famous-music-406080|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/publishing/1084866/updated-sony-led-group-closes-purchase-of-emi-music-publishing|title=Updated: Sony-Led Group Closes Purchase of EMI Music Publishing|last=Christman|first=Ed|date=29 June 2012|publisher=Billboard|language=en|accessdate=26 July 2015|archive-date=2013-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509050153/http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/publishing/1084866/updated-sony-led-group-closes-purchase-of-emi-music-publishing|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年5月，[[索尼/聯合電視音樂出版|索尼/聯合電視音樂出版]]将其在EMI音樂出版的股份增加至90%，邁克爾·傑克遜遺產管理委員會拥有其余10%<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sony Agrees to Buy Additional 60 Percent Stake in EMI Music Publishing, Now to Own 90 Percent|url=https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/8457179/sony-buys-additional-60-percent-stake-in-emi-music-publishing|work=Billboard|date=2018-05-21|accessdate=2019-01-30|last=cstutz|archive-date=2018-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180524071018/https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/8457179/sony-buys-additional-60-percent-stake-in-emi-music-publishing|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年7月，索尼以2.875亿美元收购了邁克爾·傑克遜遺產管理委員會所拥有的股份<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sony Completes Acquisition of Michael Jackson Estate's Share of EMI Music Publishing|url=https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/8467903/sony-completes-acquisition-of-michael-jackson-estates-share-of-emi-music|work=Billboard|date=2018-07-31|accessdate=2019-01-30|last=lars.brandle|archive-date=2018-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181210122224/https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/8467903/sony-completes-acquisition-of-michael-jackson-estates-share-of-emi-music|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年11月，索尼完成收购，EMI音樂出版将完全合并进[[索尼/聯合電視音樂出版|索尼/聯合電視音樂出版]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sony Completes Acquisition Of EMI Music Publishing Despite Indie Objections|url=https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/record-labels/8484946/sony-completes-acquistion-of-emi-music-publishing-despite|work=Billboard|date=2018-11-14|accessdate=2019-01-30|last=marc.schneider|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225151038/https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/record-labels/8484946/sony-completes-acquistion-of-emi-music-publishing-despite|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 營運 ==
EMI音樂出版管理超過130萬首歌曲的版權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-01-10/sony-has-no-plans-to-sell-music-publishing-business-lynton-says|title=Sony Has No Plans to Sell Music Publishing Business, Lynton Says|last=Shaw|first=Lucas|last2=Sakoui|first2=Anousha|date=11 January 2015|publisher=Bloomberg|language=en|accessdate=27 July 2015|archive-date=2015-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150730023018/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-01-10/sony-has-no-plans-to-sell-music-publishing-business-lynton-says|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括[[鼠來寶_(DJ)|鼠來寶]]、[[蒂莫·馬斯|蒂莫·馬斯]]、[[龍之樂隊|龍之樂隊]]、[[麥加帝斯|麥加帝斯]]、[[黑眼豆豆|黑眼豆豆]]、[[街區派對|街區派對]]、[[我的另類羅曼史|我的另類羅曼史]]、[[艾維奇|艾維奇]]、[[夸拉雷希|夸拉雷希]]、[[七級煉獄|七級煉獄]]、[[滑結樂團|滑結樂團]]、[[工藝大師|工藝大師]]及[[尚恩·保羅|尚恩·保羅]]的曲庫。

== 獎項 ==
EMI音樂出版曾經連續超過十年奪得《[[音樂一週|音樂一週]]》年度最佳出版社獎。在2009年，這個獎項首次由EMI音樂出版及[[環球音樂出版集團|環球音樂出版集團]]共同獲得。

